1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Have you ever wondered what life looks like on the far side of the Earth?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Welcome to Antipode: DayDreamNight—connecting people across day and night.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Inspired by antipodes—two places directly opposite each other—Antipode brings distant hemispheres together.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
On the Home feed, each video captures a real moment from another part of the world, with a switchable Day–Night mode.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Navigation is intuitive: swipe left to skip and swipe right to appreciate and open a creator’s profile.

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Swipe up or down to move between moments—traveling across stories with ease.

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Creating your own moment is just as seamless.

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Switch cameras, record, pause, or save drafts effortlessly.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Add text, tags, and share your perspective with the world.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Stay connected through your Friends feed and expressive user profiles.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Chat brings conversations to life with clear, modern messaging.

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
On the Profile page, users can explore creators through clean galleries of grids, drafts, and tagged videos.

13
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:51,000
And to ensure everyone can enjoy the experience…

14
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Antipode supports diverse viewing needs with screen narration, subtitles, and high-contrast mode.

15
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Keyboard controls make navigation easy on desktop with simple arrow-key shortcuts.

16
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Users can fine-tune playback with adjustable brightness, contrast, saturation, and speed.

17
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
We welcome users from every corner of the world.

18
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:11,000
The interface and subtitles can switch languages—English or Chinese—for a familiar, comfortable experience.

19
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Antipode opens a new way to experience life across the globe—turning everyday stories into global connections.

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:21,000
Our interactive prototype is complete and ready for presentation.

21
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,000
Thank you for watching.